"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104air1665702666109.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/air1665702666109.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/air1665702666109.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"air1665702666109\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $disable\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"air1665702666109___disable_259277\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Disables a menu item in a menu object.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"air1665702666109__topic_d81989e1_d81990e1_d81991e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"air1665702666109__p_d81992e1_d81993e1_d81994e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$disable</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"air1665702666109__p_d81995e1_d81996e1_d81997e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">set</span> | <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">reset</span>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$disable</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"air1665702666109__topic_d54072e1_d54073e1_d54074e1_d54075e1_d54076e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1221196e78\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"air1665702666109__table_d8315e1_d8316e1_d8317e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\"></span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"air1665702666109__table_d8315e1_d8316e1_d8317e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"air1665702666109__table_d8315e1_d8316e1_d8317e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"air1665702666109__table_d8315e1_d8316e1_d8317e1__entry__1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"air1665702666109__table_d8315e1_d8316e1_d8317e1__entry__2\">\n Menu item is selectable\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"air1665702666109__table_d8315e1_d8316e1_d8317e1__entry__1\">\n 1\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"air1665702666109__table_d8315e1_d8316e1_d8317e1__entry__2\">\n Menu item is currently not selectable\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"air1665702666109__p_d82001e1_d82002e1_d82003e1\">If an error occurs, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains the exact error.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"air1665702666109__topic_d54077e1_d54078e1_d54079e1_d54080e1_d54081e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1221196e135\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"air1665702666109__d6620e20\">Use only in the preDisplay trigger of Menu objects.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"air1665702666109__topic_d54082e1_d54083e1_d54084e1_d54085e1_d54086e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1221196e144\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"air1665702666109__p_d82013e1_d82014e1_d82015e1\">The function <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$disable</span> is used to disable (or enable) a menu item</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"air1665702666109__li_d33971e1_d33972e1_d33973e1\">Set the value to 1 to disable the menu item so it cannot be selected; the menu accelerator key is also disabled. the disabled menu item is dimmed when the menu is displayed.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"air1665702666109__li_d33974e1_d33975e1_d33976e1\">Set the value to 0 to enable the menu item.\n </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"air1665702666109__p_d82016e1_d82017e1_d82018e1\">You can also use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$disable</span> as the target in the left side of an assignment. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">$disable=!$disable\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"air1665702666109__p_d82019e1_d82020e1_d82021e1\">Since <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$disable</span> is essentially a Boolean function, when Expression evaluates to a non-zero value, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$disable</span> becomes 1.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"air1665702666109__section_inj_c25_zbc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1221196e185\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$disable</span></h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example disables a menu item:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"air1665702666109__pre_w4s_c25_zbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger preDisplay\n set $disable\nend; preDisplay</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ukk1665702596834.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>reset</a><p>Reset the value of the specified ProcScript function to 0.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eww1719683180873.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>set</a><p>Set the value of the specified ProcScript function to 1 (TRUE).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sqy1665702665979.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$check</a><p>Return or set the checked status of a menu item.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sed1665702666179.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$hide</a><p>Return or set the display status of a menu item.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/prp1665702665837.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Option: Copy Description and Comments</a><p>Determines whether the new implementation should use the description and comments defined in the component's specification.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ckm1665702665911.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger preDisplay</a><p>System trigger that is executed before a menu or menu item is displayed.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eji1665703130687.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger option</a><p>Trigger for handling the processing that should occur after a menu item is selected.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525712\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2525712\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$disable Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $disable Disables a menu item in a menu object. $disable set | reset $disable Return Values Table 1. Value Meaning 0 Menu item is selectable 1 Menu item is currently not selectable If an error occurs, $procerror contains the exact error. Use Use only in the preDisplay trigger of Menu objects. Description The function $disable is used to disable (or enable) a menu item Set the value to 1 to disable the menu item so it cannot be selected; the menu accelerator key is also disabled. the disabled menu item is dimmed when the menu is displayed. Set the value to 0 to enable the menu item. You can also use $disable as the target in the left side of an assignment. For example: $disable=!$disable Copy Since $disable is essentially a Boolean function, when Expression evaluates to a non-zero value, $disable becomes 1. Example: Using $disable The following example disables a menu item: trigger preDisplay set $disable end; preDisplay Copy Related Links reset Reset the value of the specified ProcScript function to 0. set Set the value of the specified ProcScript function to 1 (TRUE). $check Return or set the checked status of a menu item. $hide Return or set the display status of a menu item. Option: Copy Description and Comments Determines whether the new implementation should use the description and comments defined in the component's specification. trigger preDisplay System trigger that is executed before a menu or menu item is displayed. trigger option Trigger for handling the processing that should occur after a menu item is selected. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}